              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
          <tfoot>
            <tr>
              <td align="center" colspan="3">
                <div class="w-1/2 py-6">
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center"><sup class="text-[10px]">1</sup> All prices are lifetime. <br /> Price depends on the purchase method you choose.</p>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tfoot>
        </table>
      </section>
